<page restaurantInstructpage2_exp>
In the next task you will receive customer ratings of a new restaurant called Ristorante Italo. 
Please pay attention to the ratings. 
You will be asked about your impression of the quality of the restaurant. 
Now and then we will check if you pay attention by asking about the last rating.
</page>

